    "/extract": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Extract structured JSON data from any URL",
        "description": "x402 v2 payment-gated endpoint. Scrapes the target URL and uses an LLM to extract data matching your schema — send an object mapping field names to expected types, get back clean structured JSON. No HTML parsing needed on your side. Pay 0.02 USDC on Solana mainnet (network: solana:5eykt4UsFv8P8NJdTREpY1vzqKqZKvdp) then retry with X-PAYMENT header containing base64-encoded payment proof.",
